## 5. Manual vs Automated Process

### Process: Student Registration

### Manual Process

1. Student fills form
2. Staff enters details manually
3. Staff sends confirmation email
4. Staff assigns student ID

Problems:

- Time consuming
- Human errors
- Duplicate records
- Delays

### Automated Process using Salesforce

1. Student submits form
2. Flow automatically creates record
3. Student ID generated automatically
4. Email sent automatically

Benefits:

- Faster processing
- Reduced errors
- Better efficiency
- Improved user experience

